 2002-19272002-11-19,  HERITAGE,  ,  , 
ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JOSEPH-RICHARD VEILLEUX of Saint-Georges de Beauce, Quebec, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Jean Henri Picard, whose term has expired.
